â€œAfter 51 days of protests, only one demand has been met. The resignation of the Proctor is a positive response. We wonâ€™t end our agitation until the other top three officials resign. The Registrar and V-C did not do anything when police entered the campus and thrashed the students,â€ Hasan said.

